## 5. AGC settings item thật

Search:

```cmd
findstr /s /i "pref_show_debug_data_key" *.xml
```

Result:

```xml
<com.google.android.apps.camera.ui.preference.ManagedSwitchPreference
    android:icon="@drawable/agc_focus"
    android:layout="@layout/preference_with_margin"
    android:title="@string/show_debug_data_title"
