```

File:

```text
AGC.apk/res/xml/camera_preferences.xml
```

---

## 6. AGC string thật

```xml
<string name="show_debug_data_title">Show debug data</string>
```

---

## 7. AGC runtime lifecycle THẬT

TRACE ĐÃ XÁC NHẬN:

```cmd
findstr /s /i "Lcom/agc/Debug;->showDebugView" *.smali
```

Result:

```text
smali_classes3/com/google/android/apps/camera/legacy/app/activity/main/CameraActivity.smali
```

---

## 8. AGC gọi runtime ở đâu

Trong:

```smali
.method protected onCreate(Landroid/os/Bundle;)V
```

đầu method:

```smali
move-object/from16 v0, p0

invoke-static {v0}, Lcom/agc/Debug;->showDebugView(Landroid/app/Activity;)V
```

---

## 9. AGC destroy runtime ở đâu

Trong:

```smali
.method protected final onDestroy()V
```

có:

```smali
invoke-static {p0}, Lcom/agc/Debug;->destoryDebugView(Landroid/content/Context;)V
```

