# ĐÃ THỬ RUNTIME INJECT

## SGCAM CameraActivity thật

File:

```text
smali_classes2/com/google/android/apps/camera/legacy/app/activity/main/CameraActivity.smali
```

---

## SGCAM onCreate thực tế

KHÔNG giống AGC.

Đầu method có:

* permission
* changelog
* OTA
* crash handler
* instrumentation
* window config
* setContentView

---

## Injection point đã thử

SAU:

```smali
invoke-virtual {v0, v4}, Landroid/app/Activity;->setContentView(I)V
```

ĐÃ CHÈN:

```smali
invoke-static {v0}, Lcom/agc/Debug;->showDebugView(Landroid/app/Activity;)V
```

---

## onDestroy SGCAM thật

Superclass thật:

```smali
invoke-super {p0}, Ldqt;->onDestroy()V
```

KHÔNG phải:

```smali
Leqw
```

---

## ĐÃ CHÈN

TRƯỚC invoke-super:

```smali
invoke-static {p0}, Lcom/agc/Debug;->destoryDebugView(Landroid/content/Context;)V
```

